content:
Can anyone upload UCI diabetes training dataset on FHIR server from kaggle? https://www.kaggle.com/c/1056lab-diabetes-readmission-prediction
And then tell me how to download it from FHIR server?

Have you investigated how to go about doing it yourself? (It's unlikely anyone here will do it for you...) This community will be helpful if you get snagged on something specific, but it's not so good about solving broad problems. First step is probably to read the FHIR Rules for Asking Questions.
